title: Google Pixel 3 Model Number
content: What is the Pixel 3 model number for the Google store Pixel 3 for Verizon. I understand that the Pixel 3 sold by Google for Verizon can have the bootloader unlocked. The Pixel 3 sold by Verizon has the Bootloader locked. I want to find a Pixel 3, sold by Google store for Verizon, that can have the bootloader unlocked.
